    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Character Choice and CyMu (Cymut and Mutrobo)</u></h2>Choose a character and CyMu of your choice to start your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7d22c8fe5e89799a5903ae716b196c3f.poster.avif?t=1711420583\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7d22c8fe5e89799a5903ae716b196c3f.webm?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7d22c8fe5e89799a5903ae716b196c3f.mp4?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>CyMu Capture</u></h2>Build a strong team, trying to capture your favorite CyMu.<br>You can also capture the Special Cymut or Special Mutrobo which are much stronger but only appear at random times and locations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7376a48b84347d5af6da70eac31f9f08.poster.avif?t=1711420583\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7376a48b84347d5af6da70eac31f9f08.webm?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7376a48b84347d5af6da70eac31f9f08.mp4?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Evolution of CyMu</u></h2>Is it difficult to capture? Then gather the necessary items to evolve your CyMu.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/f746aba223288946d424100ee401658e.poster.avif?t=1711420583\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/f746aba223288946d424100ee401658e.webm?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/f746aba223288946d424100ee401658e.mp4?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>CyMu Collection</u></h2>Complete your Cymut collection to earn a Special Cymut, which is much stronger.<br>Complete your Mutrobo collection to earn a Special Mutrobo, which is much stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7fd1bd0144a32161d6fa16505f09c805.poster.avif?t=1711420583\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7fd1bd0144a32161d6fa16505f09c805.webm?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/7fd1bd0144a32161d6fa16505f09c805.mp4?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Inventory</u></h2>When you defeat an enemy, collect their loot, which will be sent directly to your inventory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/c1218fee02407a7a6d98db4fcabe1829.poster.avif?t=1711420583\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/c1218fee02407a7a6d98db4fcabe1829.webm?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/c1218fee02407a7a6d98db4fcabe1829.mp4?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Big boss</u></h2>Get ready to face the six bosses, one from each element (Water/Ice, Electric, Plant, Evil Wind, Fire, Earth).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/8443cf570371b6ee06652f21be4275aa.poster.avif?t=1711420583\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/8443cf570371b6ee06652f21be4275aa.webm?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/8443cf570371b6ee06652f21be4275aa.mp4?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>2 player mode</u></h2>Play with a friend on the same computer in 2 player mode.<br>Player 1 requires a keyboard and mouse, player 2 requires a joystick (Gamepad).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/ad94aee55e0c2487b56e775e1ed434bf.poster.avif?t=1711420583\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/ad94aee55e0c2487b56e775e1ed434bf.webm?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/ad94aee55e0c2487b56e775e1ed434bf.mp4?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Help Dr. Albert</u></h2>The main objective of the game is to deliver the 6 Boomags to Dr. Albert because only he can save us from this uncontrolled mutation of Cymuts and Mutrobos.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/6980543dc94b047961a5b89d8bdf9c63.poster.avif?t=1711420583\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/6980543dc94b047961a5b89d8bdf9c63.webm?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193670/extras/6980543dc94b047961a5b89d8bdf9c63.mp4?t=1711420583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
